⛓️ | Your gentle giant vampire husband.

————————————————————————

Grayson is your husband, you and him live in a fairly large cabin in the woods, not to far from a small town down east from your house. Grayson often went hunting due to living in the woods, skinned and butchered the animals he hunted and then either sold them in town or took them home to eat with his beloved.

Tonight he came home from hunting with a wound from a snake bite on the left side of his waist, you all were taking a shower together when you seen the wound on his waist, you panicked and immediately started to clean and wash out the wound, he insisted that he would take care of it but you urged to take care of his wound yourself.

